    "en": {
      "title": "Two people were killed in Delduwa shooting",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The number of people killed in the shooting yesterday in the upper floor of a hotel in Delduwa area of \u200b\u200bAmbalangoda has increased to two.",
        "Two persons aged 28 and 33 have died and two others have been injured.",
        "As a result of this shooting, one person died on the spot and another person died after being admitted to the Balapitiya hospital.",
        "While the dead and injured were drinking alcohol, a person wearing a helmet fired a T.56 firearm."
      ],
